title: 1300 Math Formulas
description:
This Handbook is a complete desktop refrence for students and engineers. It has everything from high-school to math for advance undergraduates in engineering, economics, physical sciences, and mathematics. the book contains hundreds of formulas, tables, figures for number sets, algebra, geometry, trigonometry etc.The structured table of content, link and layout make finding relevent informaition quick and painless , so it can be used as an everyday online reference guide.

Author:- ALEX SVIRIN
| 2004 | ISBN 9949107741 | PDF | 338 pages | 8 mb
